data.description: Welcome home to this spacious home, nestled in the tranquil community of Keys Gate Northgate! This impressive residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, complemented by an array of desirable features that enhance its charm. Enjoy the benefits of a modernized kitchen, tile flooring, convenient accordion hurricane shutters, and a newer roof that is about five years old.  As a privileged resident, you'll have access to outstanding amenities, including a clubhouse, inviting pool, well-equipped fitness center, community lounge, crafts area, & more. This secure, gated community provides a comprehensive living experience while conveniently located near shopping, dining, the allure of the Florida Keys, effortless Turnpike access, and a diverse range of entertainment and leisure activities!
